channel.title: 550 HD deob and cache
channel.description:
[CENTER]I am releasing the 550 hd deob that I've decompiled and a more complete version of the 550 cache. This client is [B]not refractored[/B] but I've provided a link to leanbow's 550 refractored HD deob.
HD only works on windows right now but its pretty easy to add Mac and Linux support.
For HD, you must reference gluegen-rt.jar and jogl.jar while running and you must place the required dlls(jogl.dll and jogl_awt.dll) in the client's cache location.
Dlls can be found here: [url=http://download.java.net/media/jogl/builds/archive/jsr-231-1.1.1/]Index of /media/jogl/builds/archive/jsr-231-1.1.1/[/url]
[B]Download:[/B] [url=https://mega.co.nz/#!MEFWTC4A!0hpNnaQVcQg5g_6xV923o1P7GYGE3IYtHcDUfE9Ymys]100% 550 Cache[/url] [url=https://mega.co.nz/#!9ctXHSDC!9rEESbsLs1hx9jCMyVSX4GFwmdFpRGl-coRCJ4E-PPQ]99.5 % 550 cache[/url] [url=https://mega.co.nz/#!IVN0wbjJ!DSTwbXsorHWkYXPrPfDnuIzKnewOk8nXXjl39C5tyzY]550 HD Deob[/url]
Refractored Version: [URL=https://bitbucket.org/leanbow/550_build_rt4]Refractored 550 HD Deob by Leanbow[/URL]
Credits to Hotyute for the obfuscated version. I had to decompile. Also to Leanbow for refractoring the 550 deob
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/MQjjZkz.jpg[/img][/CENTER]
